 your child s room and show your pick up tag in order for your child to be released back to you what are your safety procedures security is a top priority for kidscove and kidscreek all children are electronically checked in and foot traffic to children s rooms is limited to ensure complete safety for all children we also keep our child to volunteer ratio low in order to ensure the physical safety of each child all volunteers working with children are required to complete a background check what if my child needs me during the worship service if you are needed during the worship service the 4 digit code on your pick up tag will appear on the screens in the auditorium when you see your child s code immediately exit the auditorium and head to the kidscove check in desk one of our team members will direct you to your child s room what should i expect as a regular attendee each week you will come to the kids check in area which opens 20 minutes before the start of each service to check in your child use one of our touch screens to enter the last 7 digits of the phone number used to register your child you and your child will receive matching identification tags that are unique to your family and your visit your child will receive a name tag to wear which includes a 4 digit number that matches your pick up tag during check out you will return to your child s room and show your pick up tag in order for your child to be released back to you '),(79,'slug',0,'en_us',' childrensministries '),(79,'title',0,'en_us',' children s ministries '),(80,'filename',0,'en_us',' the creek easter weekend 0047 jpg '),(80,'extension',0,'en_us',' jpg '),(80,'kind',0,'en_us',' image '),(80,'slug',0,'en_us',''),(80,'title',0,'en_us',' the creek easter weekend 0047 '),(81,'filename',0,'en_us',' the creek easter weekend 0047_1 jpg '),(81,'extension',0,'en_us',' jpg '),(81,'kind',0,'en_us',' image '),(81,'slug',0,'en_us',''),(81,'title',0,'en_us',' the creek easter weekend 0047 1 '),(82,'filename'